org.eclipse.golo.compiler.macro

Class MacroExpansionIrVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • gololang.ir.AbstractGoloIrVisitor
      • org.eclipse.golo.compiler.macro.MacroExpansionIrVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GoloIrVisitor

    public final class MacroExpansionIrVisitor
extends AbstractGoloIrVisitor
    Visitor to expand macro calls.

    This visitor replace the MacroInvocation nodes with the result of the macro expansion.
